        <aside class="disclaimer">
          <strong>This is educational information, not legal advice.</strong> Foreclosure law
          is set state by state, and the rules for your loan depend on your documents, your
          servicer, and where your home is located. Talk to a HUD-approved housing counselor
          or a licensed attorney in your state before you act. Equity Guardians can connect
          you with both.
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

